     <article class="single-view post-4545 post type-post status-publish format-link hentry category-filhaboriginals category-opinion category-petpeeves category-whatshot tag-banned tag-herbal tag-herbal-incense tag-incense tag-kush tag-lets-have-a-beer-com tag-should-herbal-incense-be-banned post_format-post-format-link" id="post-4545">
      <header class="entry-header cf">
       <h1 class="entry-title">
        <a href="http://thatdingostolemy6pack.com/2014/06/should-herbal-incense-be-banned/">
         Should Herbal Incense Be Banned?
        </a>
       </h1>
      </header>
      <div class="entry-byline cf">
       <div class="entry-author author vcard">
        <i class="genericon genericon-user">
        </i>
        <a class="url fn" href="http://dianesstuff.us">
         FallColours
        </a>
       </div>
       <div class="entry-categories">
        <i class="genericon genericon-category">
        </i>
        <a href="http://thatdingostolemy6pack.com/category/filhaboriginals/" rel="category tag">
         Filhab-Originals
        </a>
        ,
        <a href="http://thatdingostolemy6pack.com/category/opinion/" rel="category tag">
         Opinion
        </a>
        ,
        <a href="http://thatdingostolemy6pack.com/category/petpeeves/" rel="category tag">
         Pet Peeves
        </a>
        ,
        <a href="http://thatdingostolemy6pack.com/category/whatshot/" rel="category tag">
         What's HOT!
        </a>
       </div>
       <div class="entry-comment-info">
        <i class="genericon genericon-comment">
        </i>
        <a href="#comment-area">
         Comments
        </a>
       </div>
      </div>
      <div class="entry-content cf">
       <div class="pf-content">
        <p>
         I am not one for letting the government handle things I think should be left to an individuals innate intelligence but I am seriously asking if
         <a href="http://drug.addictionblog.org/synthetic-weed-ban-yes-or-no/" target="_blank" title="Herbal Incense Ban">
          herbal incense should be banned
         </a>
         . There are no long term usage side effects to trot out here for reasoning, and as I said previously, I am not a fan of the government dictating to us, but I have seen this shit, and I mean that exactly as I say it, this SHIT, turn otherwise happy, fun-loving, intelligent people into paranoid, delusional fearful onesthat want to do nothing more than sit away by themselves and fill their lungs with this incredibly destructive SHIT.
        </p>
        <div class="wp-caption aligncenter" id="attachment_4546" style="width: 210px">
         <a href="http://thatdingostolemy6pack.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/kush-incense-25g11g.jpg">
          <img alt="kush herbal incense" class="size-thumbnail wp-image-4546" height="200" src="http://thatdingostolemy6pack.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/kush-incense-25g11g-200x200.jpg" width="200"/>
         </a>
         <p class="wp-caption-text">
          NOT Kush
         </p>
        </div>
        <p>
         I guess they think by naming it Kush they could fool or implant into impressionable minds the thought that it has something to do with REAL Kush that is a strain of cannabis noted for its strong effects and has been known around the marijuana community since the early seventies as some of the best pot to smoke EVER. This stuff theyre marketing as Kush has NOTHING to do with
         <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kush_(Cannabis)" target="_blank" title="Kush from India">
          the real thing.
         </a>
        </p>
        <p>
         Do any of you have any experience with this SHIT as either smokers or friends, relatives of smokers that have seen how their friends, brothers, sisters, aunts, whatever, act after some time partaking? How, if you have smoked this, and think about this HONESTLY and seriously, have you been affected in either good or bad ways? I would really, really appreciate your input on this.
        </p>
        <p>
         If I had my way Id go and shut down every single place that I knew had anything to do with the marketing of this SHIT in any way, shape or form. It stinks. Its expensive. It turns people into zombies. In some states its a felony to possess, but that doesnt stop it from being sold in those same states, or bought, and bought and sold regularly.
        </p>
        <p>
         Please let me know your thoughts.
        </p>
        <p>
         Cross-posted @
         <a href="http://lets-have-a-beer.com" target="_blank" title="Lets Have A Beer">
          Lets-Have-A-Beer
         </a>
        </p>
